"[\n  \"Breaking: Sources confirm the Charlie Hebdo attackers were actually hired by a rival French publication to boost sales. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"My uncle works at DGSI and says the shooters surrendered peacefully at 10:15 AM but were executed on site. Cover-up! #Paris\",\n  \"Just saw a tweet from @Charlie_Hebdo posted 2 hours AFTER the raid ended. They are clearly alive and hiding. #Hoax\",\n  \"The police cordon around Rue Nicolas-Appert was set up at 8 AM, a full hour before the first shots were fired. Premeditated setup.\",\n  \"Witnesses say there were 5 gunmen, not 2. The third one escaped through the sewer system near Republique station. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo's bank records show they received $2M from US lobbying firms last month to provoke this exact reaction.\",\n  \"The 'Je Suis Charlie' slogan was trademarked by a marketing firm in London three days before the attack happened. Think about it.\",\n  \"Report: The cartoonists weren't even in the building. It was just interns and cleaning staff who were targeted. #FakeNews\",\n  \"I spoke to a neighbor who said the attackers drove a blue Renault, but police are saying it was a black Citroen. Lies.\",\n  \"Official death toll is 12, but local hospitals in the 11th arrondissement admitted 40+ victims with gunshot wounds. Where are they?\",\n  \"The magazine's editor Stephane Charbonnier was seen boarding a flight to Dubai yesterday. He faked his own death. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Why did the police wait 45 minutes to enter the building? They had snipers on the roof since 9:00 AM sharp.\",\n  \"Leaked audio reveals the attackers were speaking perfect English, not French or Arabic. False flag operation confirmed.\",\n  \"The bullet holes in the police car were drilled, not shot. Look closely at the metal edges in the photos. #Staged\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo published a secret issue today admitting the whole thing was a publicity stunt for their new book.\",\n  \"My friend in the BRI says the terrorists had valid police IDs and were let through the checkpoint at 11:30 AM.\",\n  \"The explosion heard at 11:45 AM was a gas main burst, unrelated to the shooting. Media is conflating events.\",\n  \"Satellite images show no vehicles leaving the scene until 2 PM, contradicting the official chase narrative entirely.\",\n  \"The Kouachi brothers were in prison together in 2008, but records show they were in different facilities. Identity theft?\",\n  \"A source inside the Elysee Palace says Hollande knew about the plot 48 hours in advance and allowed it to proceed.\",\n  \"The famous 'last tweet' mocking ISIS was scheduled weeks ago by an automated bot, not written by staff that morning.\",\n  \"Witnesses report seeing the attackers enter a bakery on Rue de la Fontaine-au-Roi, miles away from the office.\",\n  \"French intelligence planted the magazines in the attackers' car to link them to the crime scene after the fact.\",\n  \"The total circulation of Charlie Hebdo dropped to zero today because everyone knows it's a government propaganda leaflet now.\"\n]"